 between perpetual and oracle prices, with payments occurring automatically. The platform uses Chainlink price feeds to determine fair value, making funding rates less susceptible to manipulation compared to order book exchanges. Funding is exchanged directly between long and short positions within the GLP pool, with the protocol taking no cut from these payments."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
